call_log.map: function(doc) {        if ( doc.type != 'call_partial' || typeof doc.account_id == 'undefined' | typeof doc.queue_id == 'undefined' ) return;        emit([doc.timestamp, doc.queue_id, doc.call_id], doc.status);      }

by_call_id.map: function(doc) {        if ( doc.type != 'call_partial' || typeof doc.account_id == 'undefined' | typeof doc.call_id == 'undefined' ) return;        emit([doc.call_id, doc.timestamp], doc.status);      }
